name: Experiment Or Die #85
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. What is out there? The question burdens me. Some of my favorite things as a kid were about space and even as an adult the scientific factual shows are just as good as the science-fiction. And a show called The Expanse just came back on so I've been thinking about space and the future alot. Are we still so primitive that we cannot comprehend?? That is the ever present question. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
